    {
        "content": "<p>The motivation for such behavior is to change a diagnostic message for when <code>&amp;T</code> is not <code>Send</code> b/c <code>T</code> is not <code>Sync</code> so it's also possible that this is just the wrong approach. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>relevant PR: <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/87322\">#87322</a></li>\n<li>relevant issue: <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/86507\">#86507</a></li>\n</ul>",
